videos.description: LIU Brooklyn's Jerome Frink blocks a shot by Loyola (MD) with seconds remaining, and Joel Hernandez nails a buzzer-beating 3-pointer for a 71-68 win.
videos.headline: LIU Brooklyn's stunning buzzer-beating win
